    "en": {
      "title": "Protest against the police from the token to buy fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "While using fuel from the Tesbwa road on the Kesbwa road on the Kesbwa road, the police had objected to the tokens with the arrival of fuel to private motorcyclists and duties.",
        "It is said that these people have been waiting in queues for 5 days.",
        "About ten Bandaragama police officers had arrived with their motorbikes and duty motorbikes to refuel. There was strong opposition from the people at that time.",
        "Then the OIC came and tried to explain things to the group but they also objected to him.",
        "The agreement was completed on the agreement for the private keys to the private keys of the police."
